Schema Definitions

L2VPN-EVPN-EVI-DETAIL:

EVPN E-VPN ID database detail information

rd-configured: L2VPN-RD

Configured Route Distinguisher

aliasing-disabled: boolean

Route Aliasing is disabled

multicast-label: integer

Multicast Label

bd-name: string

Bridge domain name

unknown-unicast-flooding-disabled: boolean

Unknown-unicast flooding is disabled

cw-disable: boolean

Control-Word Disable

forward-class: integer

Forward Class attribute

rt-auto: L2VPN-RT

Automatic Route Target

rt-auto-stitching: L2VPN-RT

Automatic Route Target Stitching

reoriginate-disabled: boolean

Route Re-origination is disabled

advertise-bvi-mac: boolean

Advertise BVI MACs routes on this EVI

type: string evpn-type-invalid, evpn-type-evpn, evpn-type-pbb-evpn, evpn-type-evpn-vpws-vlan-unaware, evpn-type-evpn-vpws-vlan-aware, evpn-type-max

Service Type

table-policy-name: string

Table-policy Name

description: string

EVI description

unicast-label: integer

Unicast Label

advertise-mac: boolean

Advertise MAC-only routes on this EVI
